DATA CLOUD
Use Case: Cumulus Bank and Financial Services Event-Triggered Journeys

Cumulus Bank and Financial Services want to integrate Data Cloud with Marketing Cloud Engagement. They’re using Data Cloud to establish a data foundation in Marketing Cloud Engagement. They then want to use the data foundation as part of their campaigns, including their initial customer campaign: a 30-day journey to welcome new auto policy holders and to introduce them to their policy and benefits.
